                <note rend="inline" type="source">882.51/1395a: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Minister in Liberia</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Hood</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1922-02-21T18:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">February 21, 1922—6 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>9. You may inform Liberian Government that resolution authorizing proposed loan
                    of $5,000,000 to Liberia was introduced in Congress February 15th.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Fletcher</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
